title: Dyer's Swatch Book, Carte de Nuances de la Chambre Syndicale des Teinturiers, 1928
title_raw: Carte de Nuances de la Chambre Syndicale des Teinturiers
description: Folding book within dark green board covers, title on front. Four pages, each with three rows of knotted silk floss dye samples, No. 26001 to No. 26360, with name of the color above each group in French.
